            "product_rating_description": "<p>When I see gym equipment made by actual athletes, I always have rather high expectations. If you Google figure 8 lifting straps, you’ll be overwhelmed with options, and that can be a bad thing, because it’s hard to decide which are good quality. Well, look no further – these are excellent.</p><ul><li><strong>Size:</strong> Small, medium, large</li><li><strong>Material:</strong> Cotton</li><li><strong>Color:</strong> Black, green, khaki, red</li></ul>",
