            "product_text_content_1": "<p>What I love about brands created by athletes is that they know what we want. They know the kind of struggles we have, and they can pinpoint what needs to be better. This really translates to these straps, and you can see a lot of effort went into making them.</p><p>The straps can look a little bulky at first, but these are made to withstand some serious, hardcore training and have the capability to withstand loads up to 1000 lbs. You’ll notice they’re a bit stiff, but they become comfortable after you break them in a little. Their durability is exceptional, so the stiffness shouldn’t be too much of a concern since you’d want straps that last and can take a beating.</p><p>Figure eight straps designed to work with all kinds of bars, from deadlift bars, to axle bars and more. They’ll do wonders for your grip, which will, in turn, improve your performance.</p><p>There are 3 sizes available, and they work pretty well and run true to size. If you go by their measurements, you’ll be satisfied with the fit.</p><p>This is another great pair of straps that’s priced reasonably and performs very well.</p>",
