            "product_text_content_1": "<p>The straps are made of super durable cotton, and the type of weave is not what you’d see on every pair of straps. It’s a special type of weaving that makes them sturdy. They even come with a 1-year warranty so even if something were to happen, you’re covered!</p><p>They’re rated to an impressive 1300 lbs., which I think shows the commitment <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/CERBERUS-Strength-USA-Figure-Lifting/dp/B01MD1RG45/?tag=wbcmb-20\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.amazon.com/CERBERUS-Strength-USA-Figure-Lifting/dp/B01MD1RG45/?tag=wbcmb-20\">Cerberus</a> has to creating top-quality equipment. These will withstand the craziest of workouts without a blink, and you can really use them for whatever you want.</p><p>The material is first-class but does not sacrifice any comfort to be durable. Yes, it’s thick and can take a lot, but it’s not harsh against the skin. Luckily, you don’t have to worry about that with these.</p><p>I also like the patches with the logo on them, it makes them look interesting. There’s only one color available, but even if you’re not a fan of black, the red thread and the patch really spices the look up.</p>",
