            "product_rating_description": "<p>I would recommend these to anyone who is just starting to use straps because the price is very affordable and you can try them out, see if you even like straps, and then go on to something a bit better if you do. And if you don't, you haven't gone through a lot of expenses to find out. Win-win!</p><ul><li><strong>Size:</strong> 23.6’’(60cm) strap length for wrists up to 6.5’’ wrists, 27.6’’(70cm) strap length for wrists up to 9’’ wrists, 31.5’’(80cm) strap length for wrists greater than 9’’</li><li><strong>Material: </strong>Neoprene</li><li><strong>Color:</strong> Black</li></ul>",
